is beginning to preach
the incoming kingdom of God,

17:55.833 --> 17:59.333
but more importantly,
he is preaching
with his actions.

18:01.167 --> 18:04.167
We find Our Savior in tire,

18:04.233 --> 18:08.533
for those of you who went
with us to the Holy Land
this past Easter,

18:08.600 --> 18:11.067
you would know that
this is the furthest point

18:11.067 --> 18:13.800
that Jesus went
in his ministry.

18:16.067 --> 18:20.067
As we follow the savior's
journey to Cavalry,

18:20.100 --> 18:21.200
we all know that in the end...

18:21.267 --> 18:22.433
I ain't feeling
real well, Momma.

18:22.500 --> 18:25.133
...that we will all be
looking towards,

18:25.200 --> 18:27.767
or in essence
we all go to the house.

